text: Jet is a hard rock band from Melbourne, Australia. They were formed in 2001. They have made two albums, Get Born and Shine On. Get Born sold over three and a half million copies worldwide. ==References== Category:Australian hard rock bands Category:2000s music groups Category:Australian alternative rock bands Category:Musical groups from Melbourne Category:Musical groups established in 2001 Category:2001 establishments in Australia
